---
---
<section class="relative min-h-screen w-full pt-44 pb-20 overflow-hidden bg-[#FAF7F2]">
  <!-- Decorative organic shapes -->
  <div class="absolute -right-20 -top-20 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-[#84A59D]/5 blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute -left-20 bottom-20 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-[#E29578]/5 blur-3xl"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="mb-8 inline-block text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.6em] text-[#84A59D]">
          Espaço de Acolhimento
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-medium leading-[1.15] text-[#2D3436] sm:text-7xl italic tracking-tighter">
          Sua História Merece <br />
          <span class="text-[#84A59D] font-normal not-italic underline decoration-[#E29578]/30 decoration-8 underline-offset-8">Ser Ouvida.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-10 max-w-lg text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#2D3436]/50 font-light">
          Um refúgio seguro para você explorar suas emoções, curar feridas e reencontrar seu equilíbrio interno através de uma terapia humanizada e empática.
        </p>
        
        <div class="mt-14 flex flex-col gap-6 sm:flex-row">
          <a href="#contato" class="btn-mindful">
            Iniciar Jornada
          </a>
          <a href="#abordagem" class="btn-outline-mindful">
            Conhecer Método
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal relative lg:ml-auto w-full max-w-lg">
        <div class="relative z-10 overflow-hidden rounded-[80px] rounded-bl-[10px] aspect-[4/5] shadow-2xl shadow-[#84A59D]/10">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523213139764-6677f5024bb0?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200" 
            alt="Ambiente de Terapia Acolhedor e Sereno" 
            class="h-full w-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <!-- Abstract decoration -->
        <div class="absolute -right-6 -bottom-6 h-32 w-32 rounded-full bg-[#E29578]/10 animate-pulse"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
